\newlabel{fig:Ng3}{{5.8}{79}{Properties of the GG model with $N_g=5$ chiral families. (a) Root structure of the fourth-degree polynomial with all the couplings on fixed flow. The shaded regions denote four complex roots (white) or two real and two complex roots (light green). (b,c,d) CAF regions with all couplings on fixed flow (dark blue) and for the Yukawa coupling $\alpha _y$ off fixed flow (light blue). The dashed black line illustrates the $b_0=0$ condition (Eq.~\eqref {eq:pmaxadj}), the solid black line the $\Delta =0$ for $\alpha _y$ off fixed flow \eqref {eq:Delta0noY} and the dash dotted line illustrates $\Delta =0$ on fixed flow \eqref {eq:Delta0}}{figure.caption.33}{}}
